snippet.title: No Theme Reviews
snippet.description: This is an unbiased, unsponsored, and usually unprofessional channel that reviews headphones, camera gear, and other digital equipment.  Unlike most other reviewer who do a one-pass, NTR provides thorough examination of every product.
